'''Umushanana''' (ubwinshi: imishanana) n'umwambaro wambarwaga n'abari n'abategarugori bo mu Rwanda rwa cyera. Uyu mwambaro kandi, wambarwaga mu b'uganda ndetse n'uburundi.

== Uko umeze ==
Uyu mwambaro ugizwe n'umwenda wo hasi bambara bacyenyeye hamwe nundi bitera bakunze kuwitera umwitero,uba wambariwe ku rutugu rw'iburyo, mw'imbere haba harimo akandi kenda kambitse igihimba gashobora kuba inkanda cg agasengeri.<ref>https://www.pinterest.com/gracetandeamara/rwanda-umushanana-elegant-traditional-wear/</ref> 

== Uko ukoze ==
Umushanana ukozwe mu mabara atandukanye, kandi ukaba worohereye kugirango byorohere uwambaye.

== Aho wambarwa ==
Mu mateka y'ahashize, umushanana wari umwenda wambarwaga iminsi yose,ariko ubu ntabwo ariko bimeze,ahubwo usanga wambarwa mu mihango itandukanye, nk'ubukwe, gushyingura,...

Umushanana kandi, niwo mwambaro wambarwa  n'ababyinnyi b'abakobwa mu matsinda abyina indirimbo ndetse n'imbyino za kinyarwanda.

